info.description:

info.name: hello-world-baxter2
info.html_description:
Hello World Baxter2

This is an example project demonstrating how to publish a python module ot PyPI.

Usage

>>> say_hello()
'Hello, World!'

>>> say_hello("Baxter")
'Hello, Baxter!'

License

MIT
